  SUBCASE B: At least one has length ‚Č• 5

STEP 3: Subcase A ‚ÄĒ Three 3-cycles, pairwise intersecting
--------------------------------------------------

  Three 3-cycles use vertex sets V‚āĀ,V‚āā,V‚āÉ with |VŠĶĘ|=3.
  By őĪ‚āā=0: VŠĶĘ ‚ą© V‚Īľ ‚Č† ‚ąÖ for all i,j.

  By Helly's property for finite sets, two sub-patterns:

  Pattern (a): ‚ąÉ common vertex v ‚ąą V‚āĀ‚ą©V‚āā‚ą©V‚āÉ.
    C‚āĀ = v‚Üía‚Üíb‚Üív
